<p><b>Grow Mandi</b> is an e-commerce platform which can be used by Sellers and Buyers to buy and sell agricultural commodities and processed commodities. Farmers/Sellers can put their produce as a product for sale on this platform with all required details. These products will be made visible to buyers for purchase. After a deal is made, the buyer will pay to Grow Indigo through RTGS/other digital payment method and the payment to the seller will be made by Grow Indigo within 7 days after receiving payment from buyer. Grow Mandi may provide assistance for quality checking, logistics, storage, aggregation, tracking, coordination etc. It will help the sellers and buyers to connect and have smooth transactions with better price realization in one place.</p>
